---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Our Services"
  description="Central Coast Windows offers thermally broken aluminium window supply, residential installation, and custom design consultation across Sydney, Central Coast, and Newcastle."
  currentPage="services"
>

  <!-- Page header -->
  <section style="padding: 80px 0 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border)">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">What We Offer</p>
      <h1 class="section-heading">Our Services</h1>
      <p class="section-sub">From initial consultation through to final installation, we handle the full process. No handoffs, no confusion — just one team that knows windows.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service 1: Supply -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-card">
        <img
          class="service-card-img"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154526-990dced4db0d?w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Thermally broken aluminium window frames"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <span class="section-label">01</span>
          <h2>Thermally Broken Window Supply</h2>
          <p>We supply premium thermally broken aluminium windows engineered to eliminate heat transfer and cold bridging. Every unit we supply meets Australian energy performance standards and is designed to deliver year-round comfort without compromising on aesthetics.</p>
          <p>Our windows feature a high-performance polyamide thermal break within the aluminium frame — a non-conductive barrier that stops heat from moving through the frame. Combined with the right glass specification, they deliver dramatically improved U-values compared to standard aluminium.</p>

          <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top: 32px">
            <h3>What's Included</h3>
            <p>Full product specification, frame profiles, glass configuration selection, colour and finish options, and delivery coordination to your site or our installation crew.</p>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-top: 24px">
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7"><strong style="color: var(--text)">Available finishes:</strong> Powder-coated in a full range of colours including standard whites, blacks, greys, and custom colours on request.</p>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 8px"><strong style="color: var(--text)">Glass options:</strong> Double glazing, laminated, tinted, low-e coatings — we'll help you select based on orientation, performance goals, and budget.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 2: Standard aluminium -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <img
          class="service-card-img"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505693416388-ac5ce068fe85?w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Modern home with aluminium windows"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <span class="section-label">02</span>
          <h2>Standard Aluminium Windows</h2>
          <p>Not every project needs a premium thermal-break system. For many homes and renovations, standard aluminium windows are the right fit, offering a clean look, reliable durability, and a more accessible price point.</p>
          <p>We help homeowners, renovators, and builders choose practical aluminium window systems that suit the style of the property and the scope of the job, without overcomplicating the process.</p>

          <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top: 32px">
            <h3>Best Suited For</h3>
            <p>Renovations, investment properties, straightforward replacements, new builds, and projects where durability, appearance, and budget need to stay in balance.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 3: Commercial -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <img
          class="service-card-img"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Commercial building with aluminium windows"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <span class="section-label">03</span>
          <h2>Commercial Windows</h2>
          <p>We also support commercial and mixed-use projects that need practical aluminium window solutions, clear communication, and products suited to the demands of the site. That can include retail spaces, hospitality venues, offices, education settings, and other larger-scale work.</p>
          <p>Whether you need support with supply, product selection, or installation planning, we can work with you to deliver a solution that matches the project brief, finish requirements, and timeline.</p>

          <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top: 32px">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-icon">🏬</div>
              <h3>Retail & Shopfronts</h3>
              <p>Window systems for customer-facing spaces where appearance, durability, and practical performance all matter.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-icon">🏢</div>
              <h3>Offices & Mixed-Use</h3>
              <p>Clean, modern aluminium systems suited to offices, developments, and projects with multiple occupancy types.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-icon">🛠️</div>
              <h3>Builder Coordination</h3>
              <p>Clear quoting, dependable supply, and straightforward communication through the planning and delivery stages.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 4: Installation -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <img
          class="service-card-img"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581578731548-c64695cc6952?w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Professional window installation"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <span class="section-label">04</span>
          <h2>Residential Installation</h2>
          <p>Our installation team fits windows directly into your home with a precision, draught-conscious finish. Whether you're replacing a single window or upgrading your entire home, we manage the process from removal through to completion.</p>
          <p>We work with homeowners undertaking renovations as well as builders working on new constructions. Coordination is simple, we show up, we do the work properly, and we leave the site clean.</p>

          <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top: 32px">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-icon">🏠</div>
              <h3>Single Room Upgrades</h3>
              <p>Replacing one or two windows? We handle smaller jobs with the same care as full-home projects.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-icon">🏗️</div>
              <h3>Full-Home Replacements</h3>
              <p>Complete window upgrades coordinated efficiently to minimise disruption to your household.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-icon">🔨</div>
              <h3>New Build Supply & Fit</h3>
              <p>Working with a builder? We can supply and install to suit the agreed specification and project timeline.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service 5: Consultation -->
      <div class="service-card">
        <img
          class="service-card-img"
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7?w=1200&q=80"
          alt="Project consultation for windows"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="service-card-body">
          <span class="section-label">05</span>
          <h2>Custom Design & Consultation</h2>
          <p>Not sure where to start? That's what we're here for. Our consultation process helps you understand your options across frame profiles, glass specifications, opening types, and finishes, all balanced against your budget, performance goals, and the kind of project you're working on.</p>
          <p>There's no one-size-fits-all answer in window selection. A high-performance family home needs a different solution to an investment property or a commercial tenancy. We help you make the right call for the job in front of you.</p>

          <div class="highlight-box" style="margin-top: 32px">
            <h3>What to Expect</h3>
            <p>A no-pressure conversation about your project. We'll assess your requirements, explain the options clearly, recommend the right direction, and provide a straightforward quote without the sales fluff.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="cta-section">
    <p class="section-label">Get Started</p>
    <h2 class="section-heading">Ready for a Quote?</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Tell us about your project and we'll come back to you quickly with a clear, no-obligation quote.</p>
    <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
      <a href="/science" class="btn-outline">Learn How They Work</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
